So, how did you meet?

2
00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:06.666
Kill this little beast for me

3
00:00:07.466 --> 00:00:09.000
How did I get here?

4
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:10.733
Dare to provoke our Dong family

5
00:00:10.733 --> 00:00:12.000
Kill him for me

6
00:00:16.666 --> 00:00:18.000
You wait for me.

7
00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:23.933
Xiaolong, your father and I have been together for a long time

8
