19
00:00:50.566 --> 00:00:52.200
Are you trying to humiliate me?

20
00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:54.266
Why don't you even listen to me?

21
00:00:54.266 --> 00:00:55.500
Anything else will do

22
00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:56.766
There is no negotiation on this matter.

23
00:00:56.766 --> 00:00:57.933
I'm dead

24
00:00:57.933 --> 00:00:59.466
